---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Lead Qualification | AI-Powered Solutions"
  description="Transform your lead qualification process with AI-powered conversational agents."
>
  <div class="pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Transform Lead Qualification with AI-Powered Solutions
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-white-600 mb-12">
          In today's competitive market, capturing and qualifying leads efficiently is crucial for businesses to thrive. Our AI-powered lead qualification solution streamlines this process, enabling businesses to focus on converting high-value leads into customers while automating repetitive tasks.
        </p>

        <div class="prose prose-invert">
          <h2>How Our Lead Qualification Solution Works</h2>
          
          <h3>1. AI Tailored to Your Business</h3>
          <p>
            Our AI conversational agents are customized to reflect your brand's unique tone and style, ensuring seamless and natural interactions:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Learning Your Voice: The AI is trained on your brand's messaging, FAQs, and knowledge base.</li>
            <li>Deep Understanding: The AI understands your offerings, pricing models, and processes.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>2. Smart and Natural Conversations</h3>
          <p>
            The AI engages leads like a real team member would, asking thoughtful questions to understand their needs and preferences:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Intelligent Questioning: "What is your timeline?" or "What specific requirements do you have?"</li>
            <li>Tailored Recommendations: Based on responses, providing customized solutions.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>3. Automated Lead Qualification</h3>
          <p>
            Effortlessly identify and prioritize high-value leads while saving time:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Filter and Prioritize: Identify hot leads through qualifying questions.</li>
            <li>Redirect Unqualified Leads: Politely dismiss or redirect to self-help resources.</li>
            <li>Seamless Integration: Guide qualified leads through automated booking systems.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>4. Multilingual and Scalable</h3>
          <p>
            Handle inquiries across diverse languages and at any scale:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>100+ Languages Support: Engage with customers globally.</li>
            <li>Scale Effortlessly: Handle conversations in real-time, 24/7.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>5. Full Integration with Your Tools</h3>
          <p>
            Seamlessly integrates into your existing tools and workflows:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>CRM Integration: Connect with Salesforce, HubSpot, and more.</li>
            <li>Booking and Scheduling: Sync with your calendar systems.</li>
            <li>Notifications: Send email or SMS updates automatically.</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="mt-12 text-center">
            <a 
              href="/demo" 
              class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0d9488] to-[#3b82f6] text-white rounded-lg font-semibold hover:from-[#0b847a] hover:to-[#2563eb] transition-all duration-200 transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg"
            >
              Get Started with AI Lead Qualification
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  .prose h2 {
    color: white;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .prose h3 {
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .prose p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .prose ul {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    list-style-type: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>